        <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_mutex" kindref="compound">Mutex</ref> lock function. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>This function locks the mutex by calling RTOS function k_mutex_lock. If the mutex is locked by another thread, the calling thread waits until the mutex becomes available. <ref refid="class_mutex" kindref="compound">Mutex</ref> value is set to 0. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
