        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>timeout</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The time period to wait for semaphore signal</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 <ref refid="class_mutex" kindref="compound">Mutex</ref> locked </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>EBUSY Returned without waiting, </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>EAGAIN Waiting period timed out, or the semaphore was reset during the waiting period.</para>
</simplesect>
This function locks the mutex by calling RTOS function k_mutex_lock with timeout. If the mutex is locked by another thread, the calling thread waits until the mutex becomes available or until a timeout occurs. </para>
